data.description: Welcome home to this charming Mableton, GA beauty nestled in a peaceful gated community. This home is open concept living at its finest offering 2 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a flexible upstairs loft space perfect for an office work space or relaxation.   This sleek retreat has upgraded flooring on the main level, a stylish eat-in kitchen overlooking a sun-drenched living room, an upstairs flex space, and updated modern light fixtures. Enjoy the private backyard perfect for relaxing quiet mornings and unwinding in the evenings.    This home is where comfort meets convenience to major highway access to schools, parks, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Located just minutes away from The Battery Atlanta home to the Atlanta Braves Stadium, Cumberland Mall, Silver Comet Trail, and so much more!
